               <msContents>
                  <summary>I) Maṣḥafa gǝnzat “Book of the Funeral Ritual” (fols. 3r-123v)&#xD; -
                     Homily by ʾabuna Salāmā, Metropolitan of Ethiopia (fols. 66rb l.7–68rb
                     l.23)&#xD; - Homily by St Jacob of Serug on funeral of priests and deacons
                     (fols. 75ra l.2–78rb l.5)&#xD; - Antiphons (ʾaryām, mawāśǝʾt, mǝlṭān, etc.)
                     performed for the funeral of different categories of Christians (fols. 120ra
                     l.17–122rb l.22)&#xD; &#xD; Additio 1.</summary>
